lines.text: I tawt I saw a puddycat! I did! I did taw a puddycat!
Thsufferin Thuccotash! You didn't have to over do it!

[sings]
Love ya, love ya Honey. Love ya, love ya Honey. Love ya, love ya Honey, ooh if you only knew.
I wonder what happened to that heroic pussycat? He certainly deserves a just reward.
